{"id":"guide/template-syntax","title":"Template syntax","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/template-syntax.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"template-syntax\" translation-result=\"on\">範本語法<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#template-syntax\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Template syntax<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#template-syntax\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在 Angular 中，<em>範本</em>就是一塊 HTML。你可以在範本中透過一種特殊的語法來使用 Angular 的諸多特性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">In Angular, a <em>template</em> is a chunk of HTML.\nUse special syntax within a template to build on many of Angular's features.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" translation-result=\"on\">前提條件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Prerequisites<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在學習範本語法之前，你應該熟悉下列內容：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Before learning template syntax, you should be familiar with the following:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/architecture\">Angular 的概念</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/architecture\">Angular concepts</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>JavaScript</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>HTML</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>CSS</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!--todo: Do we still need the following section? It seems more relevant to those coming from AngularJS, which is now 7 versions ago. -->\n<!-- You may be familiar with the component/template duality from your experience with model-view-controller (MVC) or model-view-viewmodel (MVVM).\nIn Angular, the component plays the part of the controller/viewmodel, and the template represents the view. -->\n<p translation-result=\"on\">應用程式中的每個 Angular 範本都是一塊 HTML，你可以將其包含在瀏覽器顯示的頁面中。Angular 中的 HTML 範本與常規 HTML 一樣，可以在瀏覽器中渲染檢視或使用者介面，但功能要多得多。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Each Angular template in your application is a section of HTML to include as a part of the page that the browser displays.\nAn Angular HTML template renders a view, or user interface, in the browser, just like regular HTML, but with a lot more functionality.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">使用 Angular CLI 產生 Angular 應用時，<code>app.component.html</code> 檔案是一個包含佔位符 HTML 的預設範本。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">When you generate an Angular application with the Angular CLI, the <code>app.component.html</code> file is the default template containing placeholder HTML.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">本範本語法指南向你展示瞭如何透過協調類和範本之間的資料來控制 UX/UI。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The template syntax guides show you how to control the UX/UI by coordinating data between the class and the template.</p>\n\n<div class=\"is-helpful alert\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">大多數範本語法指南都有專門的可工作的範例應用，這些應用程式示範了每個指南中的各個主題。要檢視把所有應用合在一起時的工作情況，請參閱綜合<live-example title=\"Template Syntax Live Code\"></live-example>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Most of the Template Syntax guides have dedicated working example applications that demonstrate the individual topic of each guide.\nTo see all of them working together in one application, see the comprehensive <live-example title=\"Template Syntax Live Code\"></live-example>.</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"empower-your-html\" translation-result=\"on\">為你的 HTML 賦能<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#empower-your-html\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Empower your HTML<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#empower-your-html\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在範本中使用 Angular 的特有語法來擴充應用程式的 HTML 詞彙表。比如，Angular 可以透過內建的範本函式、變數、事件監聽和資料繫結等功能來幫助你動態獲取和設定 DOM（文件物件模型）中的值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Extend the HTML vocabulary of your applications With special Angular syntax in your templates.\nFor example, Angular helps you get and set DOM (Document Object Model) values dynamically with features such as built-in template functions, variables, event listening, and data binding.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">幾乎所有的 HTML 語法都是有效的範本語法。但是，由於 Angular 範本只是整個網頁的一部分，而不是整個網頁，因此你不需要包含諸如 <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>，<code>&lt;body&gt;</code> 或 <code>&lt;base&gt;</code> 元素。這樣你可以專注於正在開發的那部分頁面。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Almost all HTML syntax is valid template syntax.\nHowever, because an Angular template is part of an overall webpage, and not the entire page, you don't need to include elements such as <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;body&gt;</code>, or <code>&lt;base&gt;</code>, and can focus exclusively on the part of the page you are developing.</p>\n\n<div class=\"alert is-important\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">為了消除指令碼注入攻擊的風險，Angular 不支援範本中使用 <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> 元素。Angular 會忽略 <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> 標記，並向瀏覽器控制檯輸出一條警告。欲知詳情，參閱<a href=\"guide/security\">“安全性”</a>頁面。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To eliminate the risk of script injection attacks, Angular does not support the <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> element in templates.\nAngular ignores the <code>&lt;script&gt;</code> tag and outputs a warning to the browser console.\nFor more information, see the <a href=\"guide/security\">Security</a> page.</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"more-on-template-syntax\" translation-result=\"on\">關於範本語法的更多資訊<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#more-on-template-syntax\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">More on template syntax<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/template-syntax#more-on-template-syntax\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">你可能還對下列內容感興趣：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">You might also be interested in the following:</p>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">主題</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Topics</nt-wrapper></th>\n<th align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">詳情</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Details</nt-wrapper></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/interpolation\">插值</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/interpolation\">Interpolation</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">學習如何在 HTML 中使用插值和表示式。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to use interpolation and expressions in HTML.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/template-statements\">範本陳述式</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/template-statements\">Template statements</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">響應範本中的事件。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Respond to events in your templates.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/binding-syntax\">繫結語法</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/binding-syntax\">Binding syntax</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">使用繫結來協調應用程式中的值。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Use binding to coordinate values in your application.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/property-binding\">property 繫結</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/property-binding\">Property binding</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">設定目標元素的屬性或指令中帶 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</code> 裝飾器的屬性。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Set properties of target elements or directive <code>@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</code> decorators.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/attribute-binding\">屬性（Attribute），類和樣式繫結</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/attribute-binding\">Attribute, class, and style bindings</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">設定 Attribute、類和樣式的值。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Set the value of attributes, classes, and styles.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/event-binding\">事件繫結</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/event-binding\">Event binding</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">監聽事件和 HTML。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Listen for events and your HTML.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/two-way-binding\">雙向繫結</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/two-way-binding\">Two-way binding</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">在類及其範本之間共享資料。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Share data between a class and its template.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/built-in-directives\">內建指令</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/built-in-directives\">Built-in directives</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">監聽和修改 HTML 的行為和佈局。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Listen to and modify the behavior and layout of HTML.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/template-reference-variables\">範本參考變數</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/template-reference-variables\">Template reference variables</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">U 使用特殊變數來參考範本中的 DOM 元素。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Use special variables to reference a DOM element within a template.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/inputs-outputs\">輸入和輸出</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/inputs-outputs\">Inputs and Outputs</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">在父級上下文和子指令或元件之間共享資料</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Share data between the parent context and child directives or components</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/template-expression-operators\">範本表示式運算子</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/template-expression-operators\">Template expression operators</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">瞭解管道運算子 |，以及如何防範空值 <code>null</code> 或 <code>undefined</code>。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Learn about the pipe operator (<code>|</code>), and protect against <code>null</code> or <code>undefined</code> values in your HTML.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/svg-in-templates\">範本中的 SVG</a></nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/svg-in-templates\">SVG in templates</a></nt-wrapper></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">動態產生互動式圖形。</nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">Dynamically generate interactive graphics.</nt-wrapper></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：2/28/2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/architecture-components\n - guide/architecture-next-steps\n - guide/component-overview\n - guide/example-apps-list\n - guide/forms\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/understanding-angular-overview\n - guide/what-is-angular\n - start/start-deployment\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-07\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-08\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/Input\n - guide/architecture\n - guide/attribute-binding\n - guide/binding-syntax\n - guide/built-in-directives\n - guide/event-binding\n - guide/inputs-outputs\n - guide/interpolation\n - guide/property-binding\n - guide/security\n - guide/svg-in-templates\n - guide/template-expression-operators\n - guide/template-reference-variables\n - guide/template-statements\n - guide/template-syntax#empower-your-html\n - guide/template-syntax#more-on-template-syntax\n - guide/template-syntax#prerequisites\n - guide/template-syntax#template-syntax\n - guide/template-syntax#為你的-html-賦能\n - guide/template-syntax#關於範本語法的更多資訊\n - guide/template-syntax#前提條件\n - guide/template-syntax#範本語法\n - guide/two-way-binding\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/template-syntax.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n-->"}